high_descs: Turn around and head towards the green cabinet top to the left of the oven burners.
Pick up the knife sitting on the green cabinet top to the left of the oven burners.
Place the knife in the martini glass sitting on the green cabinet top .
Pick up the martini glass containing the knife.
Turn around and head towards the sink on the right.
Place the martini glass and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Find a glass and knife and place them in the sink.

Place knife in glass to the left of the stove, to the right of the fork.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn around, proceed to sink.  Turn right to face sink.
Put glass with knife in sink to the right of the bottle and below the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a cup, then move both to the sink.
